":"death","header":"Third husband buried apart from his wives","body":"Capt. Ephraim Hollister outlived her by four years, dying March 3, 1804 in Berlin, Connecticut, age 79. He was buried in Maple Cemetery — apart from both his wives."}],"slug":"anna-hart-1724"}},"burialCemetery":null,"institutionsById":{},"crossConnections":[]}